### Authentication API Test Requests

### 1. Login as Admin (Desktop)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@veterinary.com",
  "password": "Admin123!",
  "clientType": "Desktop"
}

### 2. Login as Veterinarian (Desktop)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "vet@veterinary.com",
  "password": "Vet123!",
  "clientType": "Desktop"
}

### 3. Login as Pet Owner (Mobile)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "petowner@email.com",
  "password": "Mobile123!",
  "clientType": "Mobile"
